          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Opportunity in Federal Construction Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires certain prevailing wage determinations for laborers and mechanics be made using representative statistical sample techniques.</p>  <p>The Government Accountability Office shall study, and report on, the implementation of Department of Labor regulations to carry out the requirement of this bill.. </p>]]></text>
